com.b2international.snowowl.core.claml

Class ClamlModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.b2international.snowowl.core.claml.ClamlModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    VisitableClamlModelElement

    public class ClamlModel
extends java.lang.Object
implements VisitableClamlModelElement
    Simple POJO that models the ClaML XML schema. A populated model can be used to simply generate a XML file that conforms to the ClaML schema. The class has been created based on the claml.dtd file, but it does not contain all of the possible elements of the schema, only the currently necessary ones.
